  _speaker: therapist
  _lines:
  - Of course!
  - 'Today is intake, so we''re gonna start with a couple questions so I can get
    to know you. '
  - In your pre-appointment check-in you mentioned that you have some trouble knowing
    what memories you have are real, and what are dreams.
  - So this will set the scene for us both so when we take a closer look at your
    recollections, we know what signs we can look for.
  - Does that make sense?
